info.author: Thomas Moelhave
info.description:
Peaker lets you quickly register (time, data) pairs. These pairs could
be data from a `peak flow meter`_ (hence the name).

The data can be graphed with the matplotlib_ library.

.. _peak flow meter: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peak_flow_meter
.. _matplotlib: http://matplotlib.sourceforge.net/
info.name: peaker
info.summary: Easy-to-use application for registering time-based data
